name: Calgary | An FSX Movie ᴴᴰ
description:
Everyone has their hometown, or a place that they consider special. Mine is Calgary, although I do have mixed feelings about it during winter ;)

Here is my 6th FSX Movie, Calgary, showcasing the variety of airlines and aircraft that fly into "Cowtown". This has been an ongoing project of mine for 2 months, so I hope you enjoy!

Thanks for watching! Please comment, rate, and subscribe!
